<plot>Waterfront is a spoof of the legendary Elia Kazan flick On the Waterfront with Marlon Brando. The legendary "coulda been a contender" scene has been changed it to be a scene between two deaf brothers. One brother, Charlie, is part of a shady gang; the other, Terry wants to work as a BSL teacher at the RNID. Terry's interview at the RNID is approaching, and he has high hopes. But Charlie has other ideas...</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?411477</url></doc>
